Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.60,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.40,0:00:18.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.95,0:00:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.97,0:00:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只要能在妳的身邊 就能夠安心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.18,0:00:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…在身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.37,0:00:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緋鞠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.30,0:00:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.79,0:00:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先把手先給移開
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.41,0:00:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後再離開床的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.03,0:01:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡女人的胸部嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.91,0:01:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.04,0:01:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  緋鞠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.32,0:01:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是故意的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.50,0:01:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.47,0:01:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好色 的說
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.08,0:01:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.75,0:01:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天河優人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.31,0:01:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直都和這隻貓睡在一起 的說？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.36,0:01:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是一直啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.28,0:01:21.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然說不是一直
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.95,0:01:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是睡覺的時候就絕對是這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.94,0:01:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是這樣的 凜子  
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.21,0:01:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種狀況下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.53,0:01:33.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還敢說什麼不是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.40,0:00:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
